Bossy McBossface is a miniboss in The Shadow Reef. He can be found along with many zombies in the first stage. Throughout the fight, he will periodically spawn up to three waves of skeletons to help fight for him. His first mate can spawn on any of the waves, but this is not always guaranteed. Bossy McBossface counts as a zombie for slayer tasks, as do the nearby zombies.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • The boss's name was chosen by the winner of a Gameblast 2018 charity auction.
  • The boss's name is a reference to Boaty McBoatface, a research ship which was named by public poll.
  • His model is based on the updated version of the Black Knight Titan.
  • He is voiced by Mod Slippers.
